Turtonator (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0775: Komala
Pokémon
#0777: Togedemaru →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Turtonator (TCG Pocket).

Turtonator has been featured on 10 different cards since it debuted in the Guardians Rising expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Turtonator cards are normally Fire-type or Dragon-type Basic Pokémon. As a Dragon-type, their attacks normally have costs including and Energy.
